# Birthday Card — Cursor AI Rules

## Project
Single-page interactive birthday card. Personal, emotional experience — not a product or marketing
site. The audience is one person. Optimise for feel, not for scalability.

## Stack (locked — do not deviate)
- React + Vite (JavaScript, not TypeScript)
- GSAP 3 + ScrollTrigger for all scroll-linked animation
- Lenis for smooth scrolling
- Plain CSS with custom properties (no CSS-in-JS, no Tailwind, no styled-components)
- No UI component libraries (no MUI, Chakra, Radix, shadcn, etc.)

## Critical animation rules
- ALL gift reveal animation uses GSAP ScrollTrigger with `scrub: 1` — must be fully reversible
- Never use CSS transitions or animations for the gift reveal sequence — GSAP only
- Register GSAP plugins once in main.jsx: `gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger)`
- Use `useLayoutEffect` + `gsap.context()` for all GSAP in components; clean up on unmount
- Lenis must integrate with GSAP ticker: `gsap.ticker.add((time) => lenis.raf(time * 1000))`
- The GiftReveal section must use `pin: true` on its ScrollTrigger so it stays on screen during
  the animation sequence

## Code conventions
- Functional components only, no class components
- Animation logic lives in custom hooks (src/hooks/), not inline in JSX
- All colour values via CSS custom properties from tokens.css — never hardcode hex in components
- Component files: PascalCase.jsx
- Hook files: use[Name].js
- Asset files in public/assets/: kebab-case. Turntable reveal asset must preserve transparency and use `turntable-front.png` (transparent background required)

## Required folder structure
src/
  components/
    Hero.jsx
    PersonalMessage.jsx
    GiftReveal/
      GiftReveal.jsx         # section wrapper + ScrollTrigger orchestration
      GiftBox.jsx            # SVG present box, exposes layer refs
      RecordPlayer.jsx       # image + post-reveal micro-animations
  hooks/
    useLenis.js              # Lenis init + GSAP ticker integration
    useGiftAnimation.js      # GSAP timeline, accepts layer refs
  styles/
    tokens.css               # CSS custom properties
    globals.css              # resets, body styles, ambient float keyframes
  App.jsx                    # section assembly only — no logic here
  main.jsx                   # GSAP plugin registration
public/
  assets/
    turntable-front.png        # transparent background (required)
    turntable-side.jpg
    turntable-open.jpg

## Do not
- Add routing or multiple pages
- Add backend, API calls, or localStorage
- Hardcode colour hex values in component files
- Use ScrollTrigger toggleActions for the gift reveal (must use scrub)
- Install additional animation libraries (no Framer Motion, Anime.js, etc.)
- Add a README unless asked
